    %stuarttettdotcom-app#app{:detail => "souschef"}
    %section#contentDetails.z1{:style => "display: none; visibility: hidden; min-height: 100vh;"}
      #bar.progress-container.fade-in
        #progress-bar.progress-bar
      / Intro
      %h1.grid-span.align-left Problem
      .one-col
        %p For working professionals, weeknight dinners are an afterthought.
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo{:style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-fridge.png')"}
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo{:style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-caviar.jpg')"}
      .one-col
        %p Which leads to ordering $40 pizzas from Caviar.
      .two-col-extra.grid-span
        %p My co-founder and I wanted to see if digital technology could improve this experience. He led the development, while I led the interface and experience design.
      .two-col-extra.dark-on-light.grid-span
        %p
          %span.emphasis.bold-italic How could technology help busy people with their weeknight meals?
      #caption2.one-col
        %p We decided to create a platform around delivering convenient recipes suggested based on the ingredients you have on hand.
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-problem.jpg')"}
      / Personas
      %h1.grid-span.align-left Research
      .one-col
        %p I interviewed and observed to learn more about people's experiences with meal-planning and cooking.
      .overlap.one-col
        %figure.box1
          %img{:alt => "Schoolteacher Persona", :src => "/images/souschef-persona1.png"}/
        %figure.box2
          %img{:alt => "Food Nerd Persona", :src => "/images/souschef-persona2.png"}/
        %figure.box3
          %img{:alt => "Working Mom Personal", :src => "/images/souschef-persona3.png"}/
      .overlap.one-col
        %figure.box1
          %img{:alt => "Food Nerd Recipe Selection", :src => "/images/souschef-foodnerd-recipe-selection.png"}/
        %figure.box2
          %img{:alt => "Retired Schoolteacher Recipe Selection", :src => "/images/souschef-retired-recipe-selection.png"}/
        %figure.box3
          %img{:alt => "Working Mom Recipe Selection", :src => "/images/souschef-mom-recipe-selection.png"}/
      .one-col
        %p The biggest difference between the personas is how they prioritize time, quality, and cost. Each places one as the highest priority.
      / Interaction
      .grid-span.align-left{:style => "display: flex; flex-direction: column;"}
        %h1.grid-span.align-left Interaction
        / -- Filter Interaction
        %h2.grid-span.align-left Recipes for Time, Quality, and Cost
      %figure.one-col
        %img{:alt => "Filter Flow", :src => "/images/souschef-filter-flow.png"}/
      %figure.one-col
        %img{:alt => "Filter View Variations", :src => "/images/souschef-Filter-Variations.png"}/
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-filter-iterations.png')"}
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-filter-final.png')"}
      / -- Recipe Interaction
      %h2.grid-span.align-left Iterating on recipe presentation
      %figure.one-col
        %img{:alt => "Recipe View Variations", :src => "/images/souschef-Recipes-Variations.png"}/
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-recipe-iterations.png')"}
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-recipe-final.png')"}
      / -- Ingredient Interaction
      %h2.grid-span.align-left Ingredient Inventory
      %figure.image.contain.grid-span.fourSeventyTwo{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-pantry-views.png')"}
      %h2.grid-span.align-left How can we make entering ingredients easier?
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-scan-foods.png')"}
      .one-col
        %p We explored using camera vision to identify objects and scan receipts.
        %p Unfortunately, it's not reliable enough to be the primary method of input at this time.
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-scan-receipt.png')"}
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-voice-entry.png')"}
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-smart-fridge.jpg')"}
      %h2.grid-span.align-left Quickly add common ingredients
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo1{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-quick-add-condensed.png')"}
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo1{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-quick-add-expanded.png')"}
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo1{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-quick-add-search.png')"}
      %h1.grid-span.align-left Visual Design
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo1{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-lucky-peach-logo.png')"}
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo1{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-lucky-peach-bread.png')"}
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo1{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-bg-pattern.png')"}
      %figure.image.contain.fourSeventyTwo.grid-span{"aria-label" => "", :role => "img", :style => "background-image: url('/images/souschef-fonts-colors-elements.png')"}
      / Conclusion
      %h1.grid-span.align-left Learnings
      .two-col-extra.grid-span
        %ul.dark-list
          %li The tech of computer vision isn’t production ready for this problem.
          %li Look beyond the bottom tab bar for navigation.
          %li Matching users with the right recipes is just one facet of getting busy people to cook.
      / Footer
